methods.snapshot:
**Incompatible overloads text - text from the first overload:**

Sources a barrage snapshot from a TableHandle. A new reference of the handle is created. The original
 tableHandle is still owned by the caller.

*Overload 1*  
  :param tableSpec: (io.deephaven.qst.table.TableSpec) - the tableSpec to resolve and then snapshot
  :param options: (io.deephaven.extensions.barrage.BarrageSnapshotOptions) - the options configuring the details of this snapshot
  :return: (io.deephaven.client.impl.BarrageSnapshot) the BarrageSnapshot
  
*Overload 2*  
  :param tableHandle: (io.deephaven.client.impl.TableHandle) - the table handle to snapshot
  :param options: (io.deephaven.extensions.barrage.BarrageSnapshotOptions) - the options configuring the details of this snapshot
  :return: (io.deephaven.client.impl.BarrageSnapshot) the BarrageSnapshot
